### Create Quiz (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/quizzes
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sprint 2 Demo Quiz",
  "description": "Demo quiz for Sprint 2 presentation",
  "questions": [
    {
      "text": "What is 2 + 2?",
      "type": "multiple-choice",
      "options": [
        { "id": "A", "text": "3" },
        { "id": "B", "text": "4" },
        { "id": "C", "text": "5" }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "B",
      "time_limit": 30,
      "points": 100
    }
  ]
}

### Get My Quizzes (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quizzes
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Quiz By Id (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quizzes/{{quizId}}
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update Quiz (Protected)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/quizzes/{{quizId}}
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sprint 2 Demo Quiz Updated"
}

### Delete Quiz (Protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/quizzes/{{quizId}}
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Quiz By Share Code (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quizzes/share/{{shareCode}}
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Create Session (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiz_id": {{quizId}}
}

### Get Active Session By PIN (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{sessionPin}}
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### Transition Session Status To Playing (Protected Host)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{sessionPin}}/status
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "start"
}

### Pause Active Session (Protected Host)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{sessionPin}}/status
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "pause"
}

### Resume Paused Session (Protected Host)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{sessionPin}}/status
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "resume"
}

### Finish Session (Protected Host)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/sessions/{{sessionPin}}/status
API-Version: {{apiVersion}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "finish"
}

### Swagger JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/api-docs.json
